<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>404 Not found | ATAGO CO.,LTD.</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif, Georgia, Helvatica;
			margin: 0;
		}

		p {
			color: #333;
			margin: 0;
		}

		img {
			max-width: 100%;
			height: auto;
		}

		.for_header_shadow {
			height: 1px;
			border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
		}


		.notfound {
			max-width: 960px;
			width: 90%;
			margin: 160px auto;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.notfound h1 {
			color: #223a70;
			font-weight: 700;
			position: relative;
			padding-bottom: 15px;
			border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
			font-size: 22px;
		}

		.notfound h1:after {
			position: absolute;
			bottom: -2px;
			left: 0;
			content: '';
			width: 20%;
			height: 3px;
			background-color: #333;
		}

		.notfound__text {
			margin-top: 40px;
			font-size: 14px;
		}

		.notfound__text--link {
			width: 220px;
			cursor: pointer;
			height: auto;
			margin: 40px auto 0;
			padding: 10px;
			box-sizing: border-box;
			border-radius: 10px;
			text-align: center;
			display: block;
			background-color: #223a70;
			color: #fff;
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		footer {
			width: 100%;
			overflow: hidden;
			background: #223a70;
			margin-top: 50px;
		}

		footer p {
			color: #fff;
		}

		#footer-copyright {
			font-size: 12px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 10px 0;
			max-width: 960px;
			width: 94%;
			display: flex;
			justify-content: space-between;
			align-items: center;
		}

		@media screen and (max-width:520px) {
			body {
				height: 100svh;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			footer {
				position: absolute;
				bottom: 0;
			}

			footer .footer-copyright-p {
				width: 44%;
				line-height: 1.8;
				font-size: 10px;

			}

			footer .footer-logo {
				width: 120px;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>


<body>

	<div class="notfound">
		<img src="/images/404master.png" width="200" height="110">
		<div class="notfound__text">
			<p>ご指定のページが見つかりませんでした。<br>お手数をおかけしますが、トップページから再度アクセスしていただきますようお願いします。</p>
			<br>
			<p>The page you requested could not be found.<br>We apologize for the inconvenience. Please return to the homepage and try again.</p>
			<a href="/index.php" class="notfound__text--link">ATAGO TOP PAGE</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<footer>
		<div id="footer-copyright">
			<a href="/index.php" class="footer-logo">
				<img src="/images/atago_logo_footer.png" width="160" height="28" alt="ATAGO CO.,LTD.">
			</a>
			<p class="footer-copyright-p">(C) 2003-<script type="text/javascript">
					myDate = new Date();
					myYear = myDate.getFullYear();
					document.write(myYear);
				</script> ATAGO CO.,LTD. All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</footer>



</body>

</html>